{"tid":1005804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年廿八執屋發現返 2012年 六四+七一d垃圾","createTime":"2019-02-02T12:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T04:51:49.000Z","uid":62950,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cef722314d9c188fc39cba36e259b32d196a3c","tid":1005804,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fxc93t51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffxc93t51&h=7e1b36fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012年個時 港獨意潮仲未出現 再不滿泛民個班仆街 我都會去遊行(為自己)<br />\n而2012年已經係我最後一次會去呢d活動<br />\n<br />\n六四個d 係比個中學老師捉埋一齊去 話要傳承多d人知<br />\n咁拎左返屋企咪收埋囉 (唔係今日清屋都唔撚知 屋企仲有呢d垃圾)<br />\n<br />\n右下角個張貼紙 宜家睇返真係笑撚左出聲 &quot;用派對心去公民抗命&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncredit: 貼紙下面個本係shittyu出既六四專題<br />\n個條同志仍需努力手帶 又係中學老師個時叫拎返去做個紀念<br />\n我認我柒 懶  收埋咁撚多年先記得丟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n踢走功能組別件tee 係 公民黨出既<br />\n宜家睇返公民黨踢走功能組別? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日清走呢堆垃圾個時<br />\nd紙無拎去環保箱 <span style=\"color: violet;\">事關環保箱最終都係比個清潔 掃撚返落垃圾車</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件tee 有諗過不如拎黎著訓覺啦 <br />\n但著上身 一照鏡 就算只係訓覺無人睇到 仲覺得恥力應該會高過著件動漫tee行出街<br />\n所以件tee 唯一 同最後一次功用就係拎黎當抹布 幫屋企抹塵 然後岩岩丟撚埋佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前 所謂民主既運動會出席  但係泛民7.1散band後有咩得著?<br />\n真係同條手帶一鳩樣 同志仍需努力 直到永遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果班仆街話港獨唔可行 咁泛民個套就從來無成事過 <br />\n只係sales式鳩吹話比你聽 信我就有機會架啦  0.0001%都係機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 認柒 投過泛民 幫過泛民口勸人投票<br />\n但2016起一票不投泛民 , 支那仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95486363e718105f427b0fbc75d2c77b0ae4125","tid":1005804,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02851ff12ea09323a924e09e0f17dab4fd9f5ac0","tid":1005804,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"以前支那會出既六四相集, 我年年都買<br />\n2014年大掃除已丟晒"},{"pid":"c642b2393bcd447b247d8ad77ec6fc67295df0de","tid":1005804,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02851ff12ea09323a924e09e0f17dab4fd9f5ac0","tid":1005804,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"以前支那會出既六四相集, 我年年都買<br />\n2014年大掃除已丟晒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"今年先執床下底 先發現到有一D咁既垃圾係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過屋企仲剩返一把反高鐵既遮  係當年高登巴打集資整同高登集思廣益DESIGN既 <br />\n係幾靚  試好耐以前 過係街有人問過我 500蚊賣唔賣"},{"pid":"d0162686d3ccd8af0e55b0e4c8f1348af5102715","tid":1005804,"uid":219256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6d80976271d51c769b2515404047a87a91fae9","tid":1005804,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c642b2393bcd447b247d8ad77ec6fc67295df0de","tid":1005804,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02851ff12ea09323a924e09e0f17dab4fd9f5ac0","tid":1005804,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"以前支那會出既六四相集, 我年年都買<br />\n2014年大掃除已丟晒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"今年先執床下底 先發現到有一D咁既垃圾係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets