a.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過屋企仲剩返一把反高鐵既遮  係當年高登巴打集資整同高登集思廣益DESIGN既 <br />\n係幾靚  試好耐以前 過係街有人問過我 500蚊賣唔賣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"Sor<br />\n係2010年 民建聯成功爭取遮先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n15zge4j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn15zge4j&h=3e51bba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0yrc8akj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0yrc8akj&h=b4bccd42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">唔想自爆地板 cut細哂 無全相</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜家今時今日既政治氣氛 係無咩可能再整呢d野 (當初個班人原意 係將民建聯所做既野 盡量洗入香港人個腦)<br />\n先唔講 印唔印到<br />\n拎出街 比d愛國團體搞 差佬當係某某港獨組織 標記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f484152b93aa76f83f42dcb9656cfbb7dc61c5","tid":1005804,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91341e276125c547961c3250d39cf5d9510fa176","tid":1005804,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651a9852b70fb35f9a35c31fe00e368e36a6b700","tid":1005804,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:26:08.000Z","msg":"Set野買左幾錢?<br />\n利申31歲未去過1次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />